Name: PROF. WEST
Line: Watch out!

Name: PROF. WEST
Line: How deep are we?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
Helmsley told me that the neutrino
                    count doubled during the last sun
                    eruptions.

Name: PROF. WEST
Line: How can that be?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
I still can't believe that Wilson chose
                    him of all people to run the White
                    House.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Shame he's such a pompous ass.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Which one is it?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
We were talking about what a great
                    speech you gave tonight. Well done,
                    sir.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
It's Helmsley, right? I'll remember
                    that.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
(into the phone)
                    Professor West?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
Listen, Adrian. The situation is much
                    worse than we thought...

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Sir, the President needs to know this.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Helmsley, how long have you been on the
                    job as science advisor?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Four months this week.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
I would   say that's enough time to learn
                    that we   have rules here. You'll just
                    have to   wait until the quarterly
                    science   briefing.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
If this is about what I said last
                    night, I am truly sorry, sir.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: So you didn't like my speech?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Can you please have a look at this,
                    sir? It's really important.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Who wrote this?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
An Indian astrophysicist I graduated
                    with from Harvard and Prof. West, the
                    preeminent geologist in the US.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Who else knows about it?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: No one, sir.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Let's keep it that way, Helmsley.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Mr. President, judging from the
                    conversations we've had in the past, I
                    can assure you, your English is
                    absolutely fine, for what I have to
                    say.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
However through the concerted efforts
                    of the brightest scientists of several
                    nations, we have now confirmed its
                    validity.

Name: LAURA
Line:
There are too many crazy people who
                    could hurt her, Manfred. The World
                    Heritage Foundation has done this all
                    over the world.

Name: LAURA
Line: Perfectly safe.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Oh no. Not again.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
Hello?... What do you mean? I'm not
                    late. It's not even 10:30...

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
Damn it!
                            (into the phone)
                    Kate, I'm on my way... For god's
                    sake...

Name: JACKSON
Line:
They're kids, Kate, going on vacation.
                    It's not a doctor's appointment... it's
                    supposed to be fun. You remember that,
                    right? Fun?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
... I know it's mosquito season at
                    Yellowstone, Kate. I'll pick some up on
                    the way.

Name: NOAH
Line: Jackson, what is this?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Don't call me Jackson, Noah, I'm your
                    father.

Name: KATE
Line:
So what, you're a chauffeur now? What
                    happened to the temp work?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
This is better hours for me. Means I
                    can still write.

Name: KATE
Line: Of course.

Name: GORDON
Line:
(on the phone)
                    Simone, how many times have I told you,
                    we don't do Lipo on Fridays. It's too
                    messy.

Name: KATE
Line:
Noah needs to read twenty pages from
                    his book each day...

Name: JACKSON
Line: Still?

Name: KATE
Line:
Jackson, they've been really looking
                    forward to this you know. Don't let
                    them down.

Name: HARRY
Line: So this time we'll hit the Japs.

Name: TONY
Line: So what?

Name: HARRY
Line:
Well Tony, electronics are cheap there
                    and... you could visit your boy Will.

Name: TONY
Line: Afternoon ladies...

Name: HARRY
Line: Are you even listening to me?

Name: TONY
Line: Yes unfortunately I am Harry.

Name: HARRY
Line:
I heard from Audrey you're a grandpa
                    now.

Name: TONY
Line:
Why don't you keep your nose out of my
                    family. You're cramping my style.

Name: HARRY
Line:
He married a Japanese girl - how is
                    that the end of the world? You should
                    at least go see him.

Name: TONY
Line: Why? Do you see your boy?

Name: HARRY
Line:
Not as much as I'd like. DC is a long
                    way. But at least we talk.

Name: TONY
Line: What about?

Name: HARRY
Line: Life, how short it is...

Name: TONY
Line: What the hell was that?

Name: LAURA
Line: Manfred is that you?

Name: LILLY
Line: What happened to the music?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Hang on, sweet pea, let daddy listen to
                    this for a moment...

Name: LAURA
Line: You have to see this.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: It's alright Sally.

Name: LAURA
Line:
I just talked to him, Dad. He told me
                    the world Heritage Foundation is a
                    sham. Is that true?

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: Honey, calm down.

Name: LAURA
Line:
A man was killed! I want the truth Dad.
                    Right now.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
To a very special place, Lil'bee. It's
                    a lake. A place where mommy and daddy
                    fell in love.
                            (winking to Noah)
                    Remember the book I gave you?

Name: NOAH
Line:
I don't want to know where you and mom
                    had sex. I'm not ready for that,
                    Jackson.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I'm your dad, Noah.

Name: JACKSON
Line: This wasn't here before.

Name: NOAH
Line: Don't you see the signs?

Name: JACKSON
Line: It's fine guys.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
It's gone. The whole darn lake is gone.
                    I swear you guys there was a lake here.

Name: JACKSON
Line: It's okay, Noh'.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
I'll be with you in a second,
                    Professor.

Name: NOAH
Line: I told you.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Isn't this supposed to be a National
                    Park? There shouldn't be fences. What
                    are you guys doing around here anyway?

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line: I'll handle this officer. Thank you.

Name: JACKSON
Line: So, where did the lake go?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
That's what we're trying to find out.
                    We think this whole area has become
                    potentially unstable. I would advise
                    you to take your kids and leave, Mr...

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line: ... Curtis.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Are you by any chance the Jackson
                    Curtis, the author of `Farewell
                    Atlantis'?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
What a coincidence. I'm reading your
                    book, as we speak... first third,
                    around day 300, when the shuttle loses
                    communication with earth and drifts off
                    into space.

Name: JACKSON
Line: You're one of lucky 422 who bought it.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Actually I didn't buy it. My father
                    gave it to me.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Oh, I see.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Officer, can you return them to the
                    campgrounds, please.
                            (to Jackson)
                    Pleasure to meet you, Mr. Curtis.

Name: LILLY
Line: He was very nice.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Yes he was, Lil'bee.

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line: What did the government guys tell you?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
They think it's not such a good idea to
                    climb over their fences. They feel the
                    area is unstable.

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
Unstable! Ha-ha! They say its unstable!
                    That's funny...

Name: NOAH
Line:
There are mosquitos in here. Did
                    anybody spray the tent?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
We'll get some of that tomorrow. For
                    tonight just put your head under the
                    blankie.

Name: LILLY
Line:
Daddy you said you weren't gonna work
                    on your book.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
I'm not Honey, I promise. Are you
                    wearing your pull-ups?

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: Did mommy buy you that?

Name: NOAH
Line:
No... Gordon gave it to me for my
                    birthday.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Noah. Things like a cell phone have to
                    be discussed in the family.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Go to sleep guys.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
... You have to immediately inform the
                    President, Mr Anheuser. The readings
                    look much worse than I expected.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Plus Satnam's neutrino figures from
                    India confirm...

Name: ADRIAN
Line: We were wrong! By five or six months...

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
... This is Charlie Frost reporting
                    live from Yellowstone National Park,
                    soon to become the world's largest
                    active volcano.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Hi. Mind if I join you?

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line: I only got a few minutes.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
I just heard part of your broadcast...
                    Mind me asking a question? What exactly
                    is it... that will start in Hollywood?

Name: JACKSON
Line: What are you talking about?

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
The apocalypse, the end of days. The
                    Mayans knew it, the I Ching and the
                    Bible, kind of...

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line: ... and Albert Einstein endorsed it...

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
I know what you're thinking. But all
                    the governments know about this.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
If they all knew, don't you think
                    somebody would tell us?

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
They can't. Just think about it. First
                    the stockmarket would crash...

Name: JACKSON
Line: A seat?

Name: JACKSON
Line: Oh... I see.

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
No really... One of my listeners, a
                    geography professor at UTSC, has even
                    figured out where they're building
                    them. He sent me a map.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Well... Charlie, I think I gotta go. My
                    kids are sleeping.

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
Get them out of Yellowstone, man. It's
                    gonna get ugly here.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Night, Charlie.

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
Sorry for the delay, folks. But even in
                    times like these, a man has got to
                    eat...

Name: GORDON
Line: Why don't we make a baby?

Name: KATE
Line: Stop it! We're in public.

Name: GORDON
Line:
Honey, I created them. And now suddenly
                    I can't touch them?

Name: KATE
Line:
Just because I don't care for your
                    arrogant humor doesn't mean I'm acting
                    strange. He is the father of my kids.

Name: GORDON
Line:
Maybe biologically. Can I remind you
                    what that guy did? First you gave up
                    med school to have Noah... Then you
                    practically raise him and Lilly by
                    yourself while he sat glued to a laptop
                    writing that junk.

Name: KATE
Line:
Some of his stuff is actually... He's
                    published Gordon.

Name: KATE
Line: Did you see that?

Name: GORDON
Line: See what?

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
I mean Honey, I feel like... something
                    is pulling us apart?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Just stop scratching. You'll get them
                    infected.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: Something for Mosquito bites please?

Name: JACKSON
Line: What?

Name: NOAH
Line: That's our supermarket.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Sir, you have to initiate the boarding
                    process immediately.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Is this even possible? What's our
                    information from China?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
They estimate four of the ships will be
                    ready for launch.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: Only four?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
If it's alright with you sir, I'll
                    brief the panel about the new
                    development.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
I'd rather have Adrian do that. They
                    trust him. I told him to be in on the
                    meeting.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Ladies and Gentlemen, we all knew this
                    day would come. But we never imagined
                    it would come this soon.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: I'll make this brief...

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
... According to our latest data from
                    Yellowstone, the temperature of the
                    subterranean crust of the earth, the
                    cement that holds our landmass in
                    place, is increasing at a rapid rate,
                    much faster than anticipated...

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
... This causes extreme polar
                    instability. The magnetic fields have
                    decreased by more than 80% over the
                    last 48 hours.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Two, maybe three days if we're lucky.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Apologies Prime minster. He's still new
                    to the job.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Nevertheless, Mr. Antonioni, we have to
                    make an immediate decision.

Name: YURI
Line: Zultan!

Name: YURI
Line:
You shut up... when I talk to my boy,
                    understand?

Name: YURI
Line:
Good... That is good.
                            (in Russian to the

Name: TAMARA
Line: Yuri bear... where are you going?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Lilly, we're home sweetie.
                            (to Noah)
                    Wake up big man.

Name: KATE
Line:
Oh honey, I'm so glad you're back...
                    And you too, darling.

Name: JACKSON
Line: We tried calling but -

Name: KATE
Line:
At least it looks like the Mosquitos
                    ate well.

Name: YURI
Line:
Good. That is good. I'm sending the
                    Gulfstream to pick up Alec and Oleg.

Name: TAMARA
Line:
(in Russian)
                    Tell him to bring Caesar's raincoat,
                    it's in the Range Rover.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Are you guys blind? I can't run people
                    over.

Name: SASHA
Line: Hey Jackson. Took you a while...

Name: (PAUSE)
Line: We will live... and you will die.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Where can I rent a plane?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
... Kate, we have to get out of LA!
                    I've rented a plane for us. Get the
                    kids ready! I'll be there in five.

Name: KATE
Line: The kids have plans today...

Name: JACKSON
Line: Are you kidding me!

Name: KATE
Line:
No I'm not! Noah has music at 2 and
                    Lil' has Karate.

Name: GORDON
Line: Not that we'd expect him to remember.

Name: KATE
Line:
You're crazy! The Governor just said
                    we're fine now.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
The Governor's a meathead, how would he
                    know anything? Kate listen! You gotta
                    trust me over some politician. Come on.

Name: LILLY
Line: Mommy, why are you so angry with Daddy?

Name: LAURA
Line:
Because your daddy is a lunatic,
                    darling.

Name: JACKSON
Line: We have to leave! Noah, let's go!

Name: KATE
Line: I think we're safer here!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Noah, now! Kate please...

Name: GORDON
Line: I think he's right.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Get in the car!

Name: NOAH
Line: Holy shit!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Damn it! Where's the pilot?

Name: KATE
Line: Gordon, you know how to fly.

Name: GORDON
Line: I... had a couple lessons...

Name: JACKSON
Line: Did you cover taking off?

Name: GORDON
Line: Yeah.

Name: JACKSON
Line: That's good enough for me.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I'm coming.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: Come on, come on...

Name: GORDON
Line: (pointing at the

Name: NOAH
Line: Guys, behind us!

Name: GORDON
Line: I can't get it up!

Name: NOAH
Line:
(in total shock)
                    That was amazing, Gordon!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Are you okay?

Name: KATE
Line:
(brushing it off)
                    I'm fine. How did you know this was
                    gonna happen?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
I didn't.
                            (To Gordon)
                    Do we have enough fuel to make it to
                    Yellowstone?

Name: HARRY
Line:
(while still playing)
                    I'll be right there.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
You remember when I told you about the
                    dam in China? Well, it's happening much
                    sooner than we anticipated.

Name: HARRY
Line:
Hah... About time someone cleaned up
                    that mess.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Where are you, dad? What exactly is the
                    course of the `Freedom' right now?...

Name: HARRY
Line:
You know, your mom and I, we had a hell
                    of a great life... and a hell of a
                    great kid too.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
And the `Freedom' is a pretty big ship
                    you know... Don't write your old man
                    off, just yet.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: I love you, dad.

Name: HARRY
Line: Love you too, son.

Name: HARRY
Line:
Hey Herb. Get me a double Jack on the
                    rocks.

Name: TONY
Line: After twenty-five years on the wagon?

Name: HARRY
Line:
Why not? Who cares how long we do
                    certain things? How long we drink
                    booze, how long we talk to people... Or
                    how long we don't talk to people.

Name: TONY
Line:
Woah!... Harry, what's the matter with
                    you? Let's go. We're back on.

Name: HARRY
Line: Call your kid, you stubborn old ass.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
I'm not going back on that stage unless
                    you promise to call him.

Name: HARRY
Line: Promise me, Tony... please.

Name: TONY
Line: Yeah, maybe I should call him...

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
(pointing at the TV)
                    Have you seen this?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
We have satellite images. Here's the
                    sequence we've got so far.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Any news from Yellowstone?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line: Anytime now.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Guys, there's fuel! Fill her up and
                    I'll look for Charlie.

Name: KATE
Line: You're sure about this?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Kate, everything this guy said so far
                    has happened. I'll be right back.

Name: LILLY
Line: Daddy wait! I wanna come with you!

Name: KATE
Line: Lilly! Come back!

Name: JACKSON
Line: It's fine! I'll take her.

Name: JACKSON
Line: He's got to be close by, Lil'bee...

Name: LILLY
Line: Let's go back, Daddy.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Listen to me. We have to find Charlie.
                    He's got a secret map, you know, like
                    Jack Sparrow in `Pirates'.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
Lil', we have to work as a team now,
                    okay? You have to help me.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Dial Mommy's number, sweetheart.

Name: KATE
Line: Where are you, honey!?

Name: JACKSON
Line: Tell her we'll be back in ten minutes.

Name: KATE
Line: Let me speak to your daddy, darling.

Name: LILLY
Line: Ouch!

Name: LILLY
Line:
He's not in the car. He's on a mountain
                    waiting for fireworks.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
You're the best, darling. Give Daddy
                    the phone...
                            (into the phone)
                    Kate I am sorry, I can't talk...

Name: JACKSON
Line:
You wait here for me! You watch the
                    ship while Captain Curtis talks to the
                    pirate. Okay?

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
(into his mic)
                    ... I wish you guys at home could see
                    this on TV...

Name: JACKSON
Line: The spaceships Charlie, where are they?

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line: You can't make it there.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
We have a plane. We can get you out of
                    here too. Let's go Charlie!

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
You'll never make it out in time. Just
                    stay and enjoy the big bang. That your
                    kid?

Name: JACKSON
Line: Where is that god damn map!

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
Easy, easy. Watch the mic... I don't
                    know. Somewhere in my camper.

Name: JACKSON
Line: We're on our way.

Name: KATE
Line:
Jackson, things are really looking bad
                    here!

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
... it's beautiful, kids! Just
                    beautiful!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Just don't look back, Lil'bee!

Name: CHARLIE FROST
Line:
... Folks, always remember, you heard
                    it first from Charlie.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
Stay down there, Lil'! We're almost
                    there! Just keep looking at daddy.

Name: LILLY
Line: Mommy!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Stay down darling.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: You guys go! I'll be right there!

Name: NOAH
Line: Give me your hand, Lil'.

Name: GORDON
Line: We have to take off!

Name: NOAH
Line: No!

Name: LILLY
Line: Where's daddy?!

Name: GORDON
Line:
Kate, I'm sorry but if we wait we'll
                    all die!

Name: KATE
Line: Gordon! Wait!

Name: LILLY
Line: It's daddy!

Name: KATE
Line: Jackson! Here!

Name: NOAH
Line: Faster Dad. You can make it!

Name: GORDON
Line:
Kate, grab him for god sake. We're
                    almost out of runway.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Thanks for waiting guys.

Name: KATE
Line:
So, now that you got your map, where
                    are we going?

Name: JACKSON
Line: We're gonna need a bigger plane.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Just a few minutes ago Yellowstone
                    erupted, sir. The ash cloud will reach
                    Washington in roughly 7 hours. Maybe 6.
                    We have strong easterly winds...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: And the crustal displacement?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: No one knows, sir.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Let's get the government airborne
                    and... I mean now.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Where is the President, Sally?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
The whole North American continent is
                    about to perish, and Wilson decides to
                    go to church!

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
He's praying sir. Which considering the
                    circumstances is not a bad idea.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Maybe. But right now I need the leader
                    of the free world off his knees and on
                    Air Force One. Wheels up 1900 hours.
                    Can I leave that with you Helmsley?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Mr. President? We need to get you out
                    of Washington immediately.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Now matter how idealistic you are
                    taking office. You lose your innocence
                    behind that desk.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
Laura was right. People have died
                    because of the decisions I made.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: That's not your fault sir.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: You sound like Anheuser.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: A little.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
You know what she said to me that night
                    we brought her to the hospital?

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
`Tommy... I think you should do a
                    lottery. Every one should have a chance
                    to go'. That's what Dorothy said to me.
                    That's what we should have done.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: There would have been chaos, sir.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
You know what I believe, Adrian. I
                    believe nature should choose for
                    itself, from itself.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: But sir?

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: Go. That's an order Helmsley.

Name: GORDON
Line:
I told you we should have gone to my
                    parents' in the Rockies.

Name: KATE
Line: Gordon's right. Look at this mess.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
You don't understand, it's our only
                    chance.

Name: GORDON
Line:
This isn't one of your crazy stories
                    now. How the hell are we gonna make it
                    to China?

Name: NOAH
Line:
Gordon, without Jackson, we'd never
                    have made it out of California.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Where's Anheuser?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
The President is not coming. I couldn't
                    convince him to.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
So, the captain doesn't want to leave
                    his sinking ship?

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
Well, Mr. Helmsley, we just learned
                    that the Vice President's chopper
                    crashed 80 miles north of Atlanta.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: What about the Speaker of the House?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: In this chaos... I have no idea!

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
But she's Commander In Chief now. Sir,
                    I just think -

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: I don't care what you think, Helmsley.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
Your ass only made it into the White
                    House, because your old man knew the
                    First Lady... and because of all that
                    affirmative action bullshit.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
There was a white kid, much more
                    qualified than you. Just so you know.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: He wanted to stay with his people.

Name: LAURA
Line: We have to go back!

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
There is a protocol for just this
                    situation Ms. Wilson and I'm afraid
                    we'll have to follow it to the letter.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
Tell the Captain, to take off
                    immediately.

Name: JACKSON
Line: We can't get stuck here.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
You bastard. You knew it all along!
                            (at the twins)
                    You and those spoiled rotten sons of
                    yours...

Name: SASHA
Line:
I found us a plane, an Antonov. They
                    were just about to take off, but the
                    tower didn't let them.

Name: YURI
Line: Can you still fly that thing?

Name: SASHA
Line: Sure... But I need a copilot.

Name: LILLY
Line: Gordon is a pilot.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Let's go!

Name: NOAH
Line: Wow, that is a big plane.

Name: SASHA
Line: Guys, follow me!

Name: SASHA
Line:
(into the mic)
                    You'll find folding seats on each side
                    of the cargo hold...

Name: NOAH
Line: Wow! Look at those!

Name: YURI
Line: We had VIP tickets for that.

Name: SASHA
Line:
You check the main bus for the
                    hydraulics. I'll balance the tanks.

Name: GORDON
Line: Uh... What?

Name: SASHA
Line:
Work the radio and keep an eye on the
                    fuel, okay?

Name: GORDON
Line: We have to get going!

Name: GORDON
Line: We're not gonna make it!

Name: SASHA
Line: Shut up! We will!

Name: SASHA
Line: GOVNO! (shit). Help me pull!

Name: GORDON
Line: Was that the Eiffel Tower?

Name: SASHA
Line:
Ladies and gentlemen, we are on our way
                    to China.

Name: NOAH
Line: If I was rich, I'd get one of those.

Name: NOAH
Line:
My Mom's boyfriend has a Porsche, a
                    Carrera 4.

Name: NOAH
Line: Nothing we can do about that.

Name: TAMARA
Line:
How did you meet Dr. Silberman? He's
                    great, isn't he?

Name: KATE
Line:
I think for the same reasons you did.
                    You know, after breast feeding two
                    kids...

Name: TAMARA
Line:
We are not married. And we probably
                    never will... But he paid for them.

Name: KATE
Line: I bet he did.

Name: LILLY
Line: What did the man pay for mommy?

Name: KATE
Line: Nothing, Lil'bee.

Name: TAMARA
Line: What's your situation?

Name: KATE
Line: Way too complicated...

Name: YURI
Line: They seem to like each other.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
I guess... So tell me Mr. Karpov - how
                    much did you pay?

Name: YURI
Line: One billion euro, per seat.

Name: JACKSON
Line: That's disgusting.

Name: YURI
Line:
You know Curtis, I wasn't always
                    businessman. I am a boxer. Was my only
                    playing when I was a boy, back in
                    Murmansk. My coach...

Name: GORDON
Line:
Let's get this straight, Sasha. I'm not
                    a pilot. I'm a plastic surgeon. I just
                    took some lessons to overcome my fear
                    of flying.

Name: SASHA
Line: Why did you give up?

Name: GORDON
Line: It didn't work.

Name: SASHA
Line:
There's 14 on each side. Some of them
                    must still be there.

Name: GORDON
Line:
Guys, you really oughta take a look at
                    this.

Name: YURI
Line: What is that?

Name: SASHA
Line: The State of Hawaii!

Name: YURI
Line: Not good. That is not good.

Name: JACKSON
Line: How much fuel do we have?

Name: SASHA
Line:
Not enough. We'll have to make a water
                    landing somewhere in the South China
                    Sea.

Name: GORDON
Line:
At least we won't need our landing
                    gear.

Name: YURI
Line: What about it?

Name: GORDON
Line: We lost it all... in Vegas.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Can I come in?

Name: LAURA
Line: I've got nothing to say to you.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: But I do...

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Your Dad and I... we were trying to
                    protect you.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: But you were doing a good job.

Name: LAURA
Line:
Sure, if your name's Da Vinci or
                    Picasso. But if you're some young
                    talent in Podunk, Texas, sorry you're
                    not famous enough. People like you and
                    Anheuser and my father - you think you
                    can play God.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
You know what your father believed.
                    That nature will choose itself from
                    itself.

Name: LAURA
Line:
That's bullshit and you know it. It's
                    the fittest, the richest and the
                    strongest that survive.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: That's not true.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
What would you say were the chances of
                    a first time, middle-aged writer, who
                    barely sold 500 copies of his novel
                    making it on board this plane?

Name: LAURA
Line: Zero. What's your point?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
It's called `Farewell Atlantis' and
                    it's a fantastic read. It's part of our
                    legacy now.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
What if I tried to sort some of this
                    mess out? I need to know you can
                    forgive me...

Name: LAURA
Line: I need to know that too, Adrian.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
One more thing. Your father told me you
                    were the most precious thing to him in
                    the whole world... You are to me too.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Sally, can you take care of them. I'll
                    go check with the Red Cross...

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: Who can help me with missing persons?

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line:
Don't worry about it. You're doing a
                    great job son...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
That's affirmative, Mr. President.
                    Until communication is restored, I am
                    in command.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
... It seems all other Heads of State
                    are en route, however there are
                    unconfirmed reports that the Italian
                    Prime Minister has also decided to stay
                    behind and trust in prayer rather than
                    action...

Name: JACKSON
Line: Couldn't sleep huh? Me neither.

Name: KATE
Line: Anything?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Nothing, just static. Not even an
                    emergency signal.

Name: KATE
Line:
I can't think about what's going on
                    down there.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I couldn't have left you...

Name: KATE
Line: Do you think people change?

Name: JACKSON
Line: By `people' are we talking about me?

Name: KATE
Line:
Do you think you've changed since we
                    separated?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Well I certainly eat a lot more cereal
                    now...

Name: KATE
Line:
You know, you always had tunnel vision.
                    You could always just block things out
                    and write. You blocked all of us out
                    Jackson.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Do you love him? Gordon...

Name: KATE
Line: I love him enough.

Name: PROF. WEST
Line: By what degree?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Any clue what to expect next,
                    Professor?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
Once the movement of our land masses
                    comes to a halt, we expect the
                    formation of tidal waves, sir...
                    proportional to the magnitude of the
                    corresponding quakes.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Do we have any news from the Japanese
                    seaboard?

Name: TONY
Line: I called... But I never got through.

Name: HARRY
Line: I'm so sorry.

Name: PRESIDENT WILSON
Line: I'm coming home Dorothy...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: At least some good news.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
Would our science advisor care to give
                    us his assessment?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
We expect enormous tsunamis to reach
                    landfall in every continent. The Cho
                    Ming area will be impacted in
                    approximately six hours.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
... and it looks like the crust has
                    shifted by nearly 23 degrees in a south-
                    westerly direction. Here's the computer
                    simulation.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Our data also shows, that our earth's
                    poles have reversed their magnetic
                    fields...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
So Helmsley, what you're telling us
                    here is that... the north pole is now
                    somewhere in Wisconsin?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: It's the south pole, sir.

Name: SASHA
Line:
Engine failure. GOVNO! Two of six are
                    down. We must get ready.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Let's go wake up the kids.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
What are you talking about? I don't
                    hate Gordon.

Name: NOAH
Line: But you don't like him either.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I don't know him that well.

Name: NOAH
Line:
But I know him. He's really nice. You
                    should talk to him more often. You guys
                    would get along really well.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I'll give it a try, Noah. I promise.

Name: KATE
Line: Is it time?

Name: NOAH
Line: What's wrong?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Sasha told us, it could get a little
                    bumpy... and wet.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Your daddy has to tell you something.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
I know that with my writing and work I
                    didn't have a lot of time for you
                    both...

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
I wasn't there for you, the way I
                    should have been.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: ... And I am so very sorry for that.

Name: SASHA
Line: Don't ask me how that happened.

Name: GORDON
Line:
It's as if the whole earth shifted by
                    1500 miles...

Name: JACKSON
Line: No shit.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: Way to go Charlie!

Name: SASHA
Line: We lost our last two engines.

Name: YURI
Line:
(in Russian)
                    Get up! Follow me!

Name: TAMARA
Line: Yuri bear, what are we doing?

Name: YURI
Line: We're taking the Bentley!

Name: SASHA
Line:
CHTO ZA... Gordon! We're still too
                    fast!

Name: SASHA
Line:
Your turn Gordon! Go! Make sure that
                    they make it out of here before I touch
                    down!

Name: GORDON
Line: What about you?!

Name: SASHA
Line:
I'll be fine! I have to land this
                    thing!

Name: JACKSON
Line: We're waiting for Sasha and Gordon.

Name: NOAH
Line: Tamara! Open the door!

Name: TAMARA
Line: Where's Sasha?

Name: GORDON
Line:
He said he'll be fine and we should get
                    out of here before he touches down.

Name: LILLY
Line: Daaadddy!

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Thank you...
                            (to Lilly and Noah)
                    Say thank you, kids.

Name: TAMARA
Line: It's a joke... a mistake...

Name: YURI
Line:
You think I did not know about you and
                    Sasha? May god rest that poor bastard's
                    soul.

Name: GORDON
Line: What!... Did that just happen!?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
I'm Captain Richard Michaels. I'm the
                    skipper of the American boat sir. After
                    you!

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
My sincerest condolences Dr. Wilson,
                    for your father...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: I've been told of damages?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
We haven't completed the assessment but
                    it looks like we lost Number 4 when the
                    crust shifted.

Name: YURI
Line:
What do mean we can't board Number 4? I
                    want to speak to your supervisor.

Name: YURI
Line: I want your name!

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Keep thinking warm thoughts sweetheart.
                    You're doing great.

Name: TAMARA
Line:
I should have listened to you, Dr.
                    Silberman. I actually liked the way I
                    looked before that monster talked me
                    into it.

Name: GORDON
Line:
Did you know he asked for a discount...
                    and he paid in installments?

Name: TAMARA
Line: Cheap bastard.

Name: GORDON
Line:
You're better off without him. What he
                    said about you and Sasha, is it true?

Name: TAMARA
Line:
Now that he's gone I think he was worth
                    a hundred times a man like Yuri.

Name: JACKSON
Line: You guys hear that?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
(out of breath)
                    Hey! Help! Wait for us!

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: Shit! Shit!

Name: LAURA
Line:
Captain Michaels? What happens to all
                    those people?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Dr. Wilson, there's a protocol for all
                    that. You just stick to your art. We'll
                    handle the rest.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line: Captain? Where is the Bridge?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Satnam?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: What?!

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Satnam, what happened?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Do we have the latest satellite images
                    of Napam, India?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Helmsley, what's going on here?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Looks like our model was wrong.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Satnam was talking about a wave from
                    the East.

Name: PROF. WEST
Line: Jesus!

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: What does this mean?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
The flooding will happen earlier.
                    Bobby, can you plug in the new data
                    please?

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line: Satnam didn't get picked up.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: This one is at least 1500    meters high!

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Talk to me Helmsley. What does this
                    mean for us?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Bobby, plug in the new data and adjust
                    the count down?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Get me the other Heads of State.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Come with daddy.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line:
At least take our children with you.
                    Please.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
For the same reason you sent for your
                    parents.

Name: KATE
Line:
I have no clue if you understand what
                    I'm saying, but I ask you as a mother,
                    please take my kids with you!

Name: KATE
Line: Thank you ma'am. Thank you so much.

Name: YURI
Line: They're leaving without us!

Name: LAURA
Line: Where can I find Adrian Helmsley?

Name: JACKSON
Line: Move Lil'bee!

Name: YURI
Line: Let that stupid dog go!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Tamara! Come on! Get in!

Name: YURI
Line:
(in Russian)
                    Down there! Oleg, you go first!

Name: TAMARA
Line: Caesar darling!

Name: JACKSON
Line: Tamara! Get in!

Name: TAMARA
Line: Come to mommy!

Name: LAURA
Line: What in god's name is happening Adrian?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Anheuser convinced them all to launch.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Anheuser! We have to stop this madness.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
Bobby, make sure the other bridges can
                    hear this.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: What do you think you're doing?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
I know exactly what I'm doing.
                            (To Bobby)
                    Turn it on!

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
This is Adrian Helmsley, science
                    advisor to President Wilson...

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
... But to be human means to care for
                    each other, and civilization means to
                    work together to create a better life.
                    If that's true there is nothing human
                    and nothing civilized about what we're
                    doing here. Ask yourselves ... Can we
                    really stand by and let all those
                    people out there die?

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
A civilization that allows that, does
                     not deserve to survive.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
Or at least I don't want to be part of
                     it.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
We'll miss you Helmsley but somehow
                     we'll get by. Officer switch that off.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line: That's an order soldier.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Don't do it!

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
Have you lost your mind? Look at the
                     countdown. We have less than five
                     minutes left... And none of our ships
                     have the resources to feed those
                     people. If you save them today we all
                     starve tomorrow.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
Do you wanna be responsible for the
                     extinction of the human race? Can you
                     handle that, Adrian?!

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
There is a young astrophysicist from
                    India who is the reason we are all
                    here, trying to give mankind a second
                    chance. He's the one who discovered it
                    all, the one who connected the dots. We
                    all owe him our lives.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
I just learned that he was killed with
                    his family by a tsunami in eastern
                    India. You know why?

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
He died because we forgot to pick him
                    up.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line:
I beg you... whatever our future holds
                    don't let us start it with an act of
                    cruelty. What will you tell your
                    children... and their children?

Name: LAURA
Line:
If my father were here, he would open
                    the gates.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Captain Michaels, you heard them.

Name: LILLY
Line: Phew... It stinks in here.

Name: TAMARA
Line: Sssh...Caesar.

Name: JACKSON
Line: Noah! Watch out!

Name: KATE
Line: No!

Name: NOAH
Line: Something happened, mom.

Name: JACKSON
Line: We have to stop it!

Name: JACKSON
Line: You did it, man. You did it.

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: What's wrong with the gate?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Can you zoom in?

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
I know those kids. Remember the book I
                    told you about? Their father wrote it.

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
We're loaded. We can close the gates
                    sir.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Do it!

Name: YURI
Line:
(in Russian)
                    Pull yourself up!

Name: YURI
Line: Oleg! Catch your brother!

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Why is the stern gate not closing?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
Something's wrong with the hydraulics,
                    sir.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line: I think we found the problem.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line: How did they get in there?

Name: LAURA
Line:
That guy is injured. Something must
                    have gone wrong.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
You're damn right something went wrong!
                    Congratulations Helmsley, you may have
                    just killed us all but as long as your
                    conscience is clean...

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Let's get an emergency crew there right
                    now. I'll meet them at the Hydraulic
                    Chamber.

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
You think you're the main man now, just
                    because your fucking the President's
                    daughter?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: What are you all waiting for?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: There's no way to override it?

Name: LAURA
Line: What now?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Then how will we get to the hydraulic
                    chamber?

Name: KATE
Line: Tamara! Take Lilly and Noah.

Name: LILLY
Line: Mummy!

Name: TAMARA
Line: Lilly run!

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Is there any way to talk to them?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
We have to move him higher.
                            (looks around)
                    Over there!

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: What is our position?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: You must be kidding!

Name: KATE
Line:
We need something to stop the bleeding
                    or he'll die.

Name: NOAH
Line: Mum, will this do?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
(Over a speaker)
                    Mr. Curtis... I'm Adrian Helmsley. We
                    met once before. Your daughter is with
                    me.

Name: KATE
Line: Lilly!

Name: LILLY
Line: I'm alright Mom!

Name: ADRIAN
Line: You're our only hope.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I'll go back. I'll try my best.

Name: NOAH
Line: I'll go with you.

Name: JACKSON
Line: You stay with Mommy.

Name: JACKSON (CONT'D)
Line: I'll be right back...

Name: ANHEUSER
Line: Captain, what's happening?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: What's happening?...

Name: KATE
Line: Noah!

Name: NOAH
Line: Mom, we did it!

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Captain Michaels - close the gate!

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: That's affirmative. Close the gate!

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line: Engage starboard stabilizers!

Name: KATE
Line: Noah! Where is he?

Name: NOAH
Line: He was just behind me...

Name: JACKSON
Line:
If you would ever consider to give me
                    another chance... I promise, I'll
                    always be there when you need me.

Name: KATE
Line:
Whatever you do... I will never let you
                    go again.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
...   and all we can hear is the sound of
                    our   own breathing that reminds us we
                    are   still sharing our memories, hopes
                    and   ideas.

Name: ADRIAN (CONT'D)
Line:
... And funny, just today we found out
                    that the entire crew of the Atlantis,
                    somehow or another, has relatives in
                    Wisconsin.

Name: (PAUSE)
Line: The end.

Name: LAURA
Line: How many copies did you say that sold?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Less than 500.
                            (with a smile)
                    It's what you might call a cult
                    classic.

Name: LAURA
Line:
It seems we have very different tastes
                    Mr. Helmsley?

Name: LAURA
Line: Actually my diary's pretty open.

Name: LILLY
Line: Daddy? When can we go back home?

Name: JACKSON
Line:
There's nothing we can go back to
                    Lil'bee. Whatever's out there, that's
                    our home now. Don't be scared.

Name: LILLY
Line: I'm not Daddy. No more pull-ups.

Name: LILLY
Line: Of course you can. He's your doggie.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: You called for me, sir?

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
Prof. West has something to show you,
                    Mr. Helmsley.

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
The water is receding much faster than
                    we projected, Adrian...

Name: LAURA
Line: What's that?

Name: PROF. WEST
Line:
It's hard to believe, but the Himalayas
                    are no longer the roof of the world.
                    It's now the Drakensberg mountains of
                    Kwa-Zulu Natal. The whole African
                    continent has risen several thousand
                    feet and most likely, never even
                    flooded.

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
Our European colleagues have already
                    set course for it.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: This is Helmsley.

Name: CAPTAIN MICHAELS
Line:
We should have a visual of the `Freedom
                    of the Seas' shortly.

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
Dad. We're coming to pick you guys up.
                    How's Tony?

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
Young guys like you with your
                    idealistic dreams, you think you can
                    change the world...

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line:
I just pray to God, that you keep on
                    making the right calls... in this new
                    world of ours.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line: Mr. Helmsley, one more thing.

Name: ANHEUSER (CONT'D)
Line: There was no one.

Name: ADRIAN
Line: Pardon me?

Name: ANHEUSER
Line:
There was no white kid better than you.
                    I'm terribly sorry I said that.

Name: JACKSON
Line: I thought you might want this.

Name: NOAH
Line:
Do you think I'll still get a signal
                    ... Dad?

Name: ADRIAN
Line: I finally finished your book Jackson.

Name: KATE
Line:
Really? You may well be the first
                    person who ever got to the end.

Name: JACKSON
Line:
Excuse me, I believe he's addressing
                    the author. Well, what did you think?

Name: ADRIAN
Line:
I'd say... those astronauts of yours
                    would be shitting themselves, if they
                    knew all their relatives are now stuck
                    in the South Pole.
